channel.title: My RuneScape ALOG
channel.description:
If you don't like, don't post. Simple as that..
Made this for two reasons - Maybe some people will find some tips on how to make money, And for support from my family here on Moparscape :)
So basically I will be posting daily updates from when I just started Playing rs again. I have a decent acc, stats. Just no cash!
I do not bot, so I will be releasing my name feel free to pm me ingame.
Current Goals/Complete *note* these might be simple for you. But for me it'll be hard [Legend - red - Not done yellow - Working on Green - FINISHED :) Full Bandos Complete 50 Games of barrows Have 1m Cash Have 5m Cash Have 10m Cash Have 100m Cash
I used to have alot.
Day 1! Getting ready for another boring game of barrows :) [img]http://img683.imageshack.us/img683/3872/111006150802.png[/img] [img]http://img5.imageshack.us/img5/1952/111006150737.png[/img]
